      <title>路透调查显示墨西哥四月初年度总体通胀率走高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-annual-headline-inflation-seen-higher-early-april-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二路透调查显示，随着核心通胀放缓，墨西哥整体通胀可能在 4 月上半月上升，这提振了墨西哥央行将在下一次货币政策会议上维持基准利率不变的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-annual-headline-inflation-seen-higher-early-april-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 18:14:12 GMT</pubDate>
